<h1><%= @cocktail.name %></h1>
<h2>To recreate this delicious drink you will need</h2>
<ul>
  <% @cocktail.doses.each do |dose| %>
    <li><%= dose.description %> of <%= dose.ingredient.name.downcase %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<h4>Add a doses:</h4>
<%= render 'doses/form', cocktail: @cocktail, dose: @dose %>
<p>Have an idea on how we could improve this drink?</p>
<p>Do hesitate to let us know in the comment section...</p>
